----------------------------------------------------------------------
Optional Local AI Lite downloads
----------------------------------------------------------------------

NomiFun does not bundle the following runtime or model artifacts in its
installer. When a user explicitly installs a local model, NomiFun downloads
the pinned artifacts directly from the upstream locations identified below.

llama.cpp / llama-server runtime
  https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp
  Pinned release: b9957
  Copyright (c) 2023-2026 The ggml authors
  Licensed under the MIT License.
  License text: https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp/blob/b9957/LICENSE

Qwen3.5 models (4B and 9B)
  https://huggingface.co/Qwen
  Developed by the Qwen Team at Alibaba Cloud.
  The corresponding upstream model repositories declare the Apache License,
  Version 2.0 (SPDX: Apache-2.0).

  https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3.5-4B
  https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3.5-9B

Qwen3.5 GGUF Q4_K_M quantizations
  Produced and published by the Hugging Face organization "unsloth" as
  quantized derivatives of the corresponding Qwen3.5 models:

  https://huggingface.co/unsloth/Qwen3.5-4B-GGUF/tree/e87f176479d0855a907a41277aca2f8ee7a09523
  https://huggingface.co/unsloth/Qwen3.5-9B-GGUF/tree/3885219b6810b007914f3a7950a8d1b469d598a5

  These repository cards identify Unsloth's GGUF conversion and the Qwen
  repositories as the base models. Review both the pinned quantization
  repository cards and the upstream Qwen3.5 Apache-2.0 terms before
  redistribution.

Qwen3.5 multimodal projectors
  The optional `mmproj-F16.gguf` files are downloaded from the same pinned
  Unsloth Qwen3.5 GGUF revisions above and are used only for local image
  understanding. They remain subject to the corresponding Qwen3.5 and
  conversion-repository terms.

stable-diffusion.cpp / sd-cli runtime
  https://github.com/leejet/stable-diffusion.cpp
  Pinned release: master-775-b5d8120
  Copyright (c) stable-diffusion.cpp contributors
  Licensed under the MIT License.
  License text: https://github.com/leejet/stable-diffusion.cpp/blob/master-775-b5d8120/LICENSE

Z-Image-Turbo GGUF
  https://huggingface.co/leejet/Z-Image-Turbo-GGUF/tree/c61c0e422dc8b541b7548cf33a4ef8302b0f8085
  Optional Q3_K quantization used for local text-to-image generation.
  The repository identifies Z-Image-Turbo as the upstream model and declares
  the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Qwen3-4B-Instruct-2507 GGUF text encoder
  https://huggingface.co/unsloth/Qwen3-4B-Instruct-2507-GGUF/tree/a06e946bb6b655725eafa393f4a9745d460374c9
  Optional Q4_K_M text encoder used by the pinned Z-Image recipe.
  The upstream Qwen model is licensed under Apache-2.0.

Z-Image VAE artifact
  https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/tree/d24c4cf2a0cd98a42f23467e27e3d76ee9438b8e
  Optional file: split_files/vae/ae.safetensors
  The pinned repository card did not declare a license when this catalog was
  prepared. NomiFun does not redistribute this file; the UI discloses this
  qualification before the user chooses to download it. Re-check upstream
  provenance and terms before any redistribution.

PP-OCRv6 Small ONNX exports
  https://huggingface.co/PaddlePaddle/PP-OCRv6_small_det_onnx/tree/28fe5895c24fd108c19eb3e8479f4ab385fbfc62
  https://huggingface.co/PaddlePaddle/PP-OCRv6_small_rec_onnx/tree/b8f84f0b80c529de40b4fbb3544b84fa7233a513
